{
  "stem": "7777.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only like it showed that a couple years later, in the '20, they start to look-- they start-- started anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in the the town, Lemberg, there was arrested one man, Stanislaw Steiger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For they was telling-- he killed-- he want to kill the Polish president.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Only there was the court, and he was out from the court.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, the anti-Semitism was very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Polish people, they try to-- to get out the possibility for the Jewish, that live in Poland, to exist.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What they was be able to do, they did-- they put them in high-- high taxes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it-- and it-- for us, it was possible just to cut the Jewish profits they was doing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Like in the last years, like, we have in the grocery, we have Polish customers, we have Jewish customers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Like before Christmas, they used to-- in our town was a college, two Polish students stand up by the door.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This-- and-- and this was in the last years-- and the Polish people was ashamed to go in, in this thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was very hard to live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Even--it was a lot to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Like, the people in-- in Warsaw, they have the colleges.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They make the left side for the Jews, and the right side for the Pole, to be separated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this was a lot-- a lot of time, they was attacking the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The Jew don't have even the right to enter something-- if he enters something, he was arrested.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, I was walking-- it was in the night-- with my friend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was about 10 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And two-- two Polish guys was hitting us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We started to call police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Police come to, come and-- and he said, what are you doing so late, the Jews in the street?",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
